                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>and <persName>Mrs Cohen</persName> saves you 50 or<lb/> 75 cents express. I regret\n                I<lb/> cannot forward you any Occident<lb/> subscriptionsâ€”people are not<lb/> over\n                ready to pay these, or their<lb/> dues for books. The Bible had<lb/> been paid for\n                some time, but<lb/> I waited to forward so small<lb/> an amount.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I am obliged to you for<lb/> your congratulations on my having<lb/>\n                received a title and a third son<lb/> the <add>×—×•×˜ ×”×ž×©×•×œ×©</add> I trust and\n                pray.<lb/> I did not send the article to the<lb/> Messenger but some friends or<lb/>\n                the Editor wrote it. I am not<lb/> a correspondent of that most<lb/> creditable\n                sheet, and truth<lb/> I am not quite Miss nancified<add>?</add><lb/> yet.</p>"
                  },
